Make changes to food entries here!

The main area is used to browse all your saved food items. Click on the tabs to switch between List of all Foods, Eaten foods, Friends list (coming soon). Add a new food item to the list by clicking on the Plus button in the action bar. Click on the Clear List button to clear all your food items. Just tap on the name to open the food entry for changes and reviews.
